# Hugging Face OAuth — register a Developer Application at
#   https://huggingface.co/settings/connected-applications
# Scopes to enable: openid, profile, read-repos, write-repos
# Add your dev + prod redirect URIs to the app's allow-list, each ending in "/":
#   http://localhost:5173/    (vite dev default)
#   https://your-domain/      (production)
# Then copy this file to .env.local and fill in the client ID:
VITE_HF_OAUTH_CLIENT_ID=
